          "name": "Monster Core",
          "page": 301,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "High-ranking sedacthies are expected to both plan campaigns and wade into battle. These speakers achieve their rank by accumulating several large servants or a single massive creature like a megalodon.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
